@startuml seq_23_create_community
title Sequence Diagram: UC-23 Create Community

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Community Controller" as Controller
participant "Community Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Community Repo" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1/2.1/3.1) Fill community details & attach media
Frontend -> Controller: (4.1) POST /api/communities (multipart form)
Controller -> Service: (5.1) Create Community
Service -> Repo: (5.2) Check community name availability
Repo --> Service: (5.3) Name is available

alt Media (avatar/banner) attached
    Service -> Cloudinary: (3.2) Upload media stream
    Cloudinary --> Service: (3.3) Return Media URLs & IDs
end

Service -> Repo: (6.1) Insert new Community record
Repo --> Service: (6.2) Community created (ID)

Service -> Repo: (7.1) Add creator as Community Admin/Owner
Repo --> Service: (7.2) Role assigned

Service --> Controller: (8.1) Created Community Data
Controller --> Frontend: (8.2) 201 Created
Frontend --> User: (8.3) Redirect to new community page
@enduml
